<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kontak - Lucky Aldi Pratama</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl w-full bg-white rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row overflow-hidden border border-slate-100">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 bg-indigo-600 p-10 md:p-16 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Mari Bicara!</h2>
            <p class="text-indigo-100 mb-12">Tertarik untuk berkolaborasi atau sekadar bertanya? Kirimkan pesan Anda melalui formulir di samping.</p>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></div>
                    <span class="font-medium text-sm">lucky.aldi@email.com</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i></div>
                    <span class="font-medium text-sm">Jakarta, Indonesia</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="md:w-1/2 p-10 md:p-16">
            <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Terima kasih! Pesan Anda (simulasi) telah terkirim.');" class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Nama</label>
                    <input type="text" class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-2xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-600 outline-none transition" placeholder="Nama Lengkap" required>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-2xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-600 outline-none transition" placeholder="email@contoh.com" required>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Pesan</label>
                    <textarea rows="4" class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-2xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-600 outline-none transition" placeholder="Halo Lucky..." required></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="w-full py-4 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-indigo-600 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200 transition">Kirim Pesan</button>
            </form>
            <div class="mt-6 text-center">
                <a href="about.html" class="text-slate-400 text-sm hover:text-indigo-600 transition">Kembali ke Profil</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
